title: SVENGOOLIE - Inner Sanctum-Calling Dr. Death (1943) 7-29-17
description:
Svengoolie - Inner Sanctum Mysteries - Calling Dr. Death (1943) Svengoolie's Broadcast 5-16-2016 And 7-29-2017

Plot:
Losing his memories of the last few days, neurologist Dr. Steele is told that his wife has been brutally murdered. Steele, aware of his conniving wife's infidelity, believes he may have been the killer and enlists the aid of his pretty nurse Stella to hypnotize him into recovering his lost memories. 

Personal Info: The film itself is a DVD print from the Inner Sanctum set.
For the Sven Content : This a combo of sorts using my original recording 5 -16 -2016 and a rebroadcast of the same film on 7 /29 / 2017 featuring new and different Gilbert Gottfried commentary ...the newer segments are included at the end, as well as, mail segment which Sven ALWAYS has on rebroadcasts of his films. I apologize for ANY misspellings .

I hope you enjoy, requests welcome, and please Seed.
